sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Buyer
    participant F as React Frontend
    participant API as Node.js Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant A as Admin

    Note over B,A: Seller Verification Workflow

    %% Buyer applies
    B->>F: Clicks "Become a Seller"
    F->>F: Shows application form
    B->>F: Fills business name, type, national ID
    F->>API: POST /api/user/become-seller
    API->>API: Validates required fields
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO seller_profile (status='pending')
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>F: 200 {status: "pending"}
    F-->>B: Shows "Application Pending"

    %% Admin reviews
    A->>F: Opens Admin Dashboard
    F->>API: GET /api/admin/notifications
    API->>DB: SELECT COUNT(*) WHERE status='pending'
    DB-->>API: {pendingSellers: 1}
    API-->>F: Badge count = 1
    F-->>A: Shows notification badge

    A->>F: Clicks "Seller Requests"
    F->>API: GET /api/admin/seller-requests
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM seller_profile WHERE status='pending'
    DB-->>API: [application data]
    API-->>F: Pending applications list
    F-->>A: Displays applications

    %% Admin approves
    A->>F: Clicks "Approve"
    F->>API: POST /api/admin/seller-requests/:id/approve
    API->>DB: UPDATE seller_profile SET status='verified'
    API->>DB: UPDATE users SET role='seller'
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO admin_activity_log
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>F: 200 {message: "approved"}
    F-->>A: Shows success

    %% Buyer sees result
    B->>F: Refreshes profile
    F->>API: GET /api/user/me
    API->>DB: SELECT role FROM users
    DB-->>API: {role: "seller"}
    API-->>F: {role: "seller"}
    F-->>B: Shows seller features (Add Property, Analytics)
